title: ‘Deewani Mastani’ to be launched in Delhi as Deepika Padukone walks the ramp for Anju Modi
text: ‘Deewani Mastani’ to be launched in Delhi as Deepika Padukone walks the ramp for Anju Modi Friday, 16 October 2015 (6 minutes ago) Deepika Padukone will be taking time out from her busy schedule to fly to Delhi where she will walk the ramp for a special 'Bajirao Mastani' themed fashion show. Deepika Padukone Launches Her NGO On Mental Health | Live Love Laugh Foundation 02:41 Bollywood actress Deepika Padukone launched her Non-government organization Live Love Laugh foundation, in Mumbai.
